snippet.title: Paladins X RWBY | Cinematic Teaser
snippet.description:
New collaborating with popular RWBY! 
A crossover in partnership with "Rooster Teeth Animation" bringing the four beloved cast -Ruby, Weiss, Blake and Yang as skins for existing characters in Paladins!

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Pre-rendered cinematic done for Paladins, introducing new character collaboration from RWBY.
Client: Hi-Rez Studios, Evil Moji Games 

More info on our website:
https://glow-production.com/project/paladins-x-rwby/
